data.name: 0000 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I started using Nagato's mop to erase the singularities, just as I did before.

data.name: 0001 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Please be as quick as you can. Miss Suzumiya will return before long.

data.name: 0002 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Yeah, I get it.

data.name: 0003 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: What would Haruhi see if she came back now?

data.name: 0004 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: An empty hallway? The entrance to class 1-10?

data.name: 0005 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Seriously, if she came in here, what would become of the world?

data.name: 0006 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I absolutely cannot accept a world where such strange things are normal.

data.name: 0007 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Or even worse, the destruction of the world, right?

data.name: 0008 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I put force into my mopping arm while thinking about that.

data.name: 0009 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Not that I have any idea if mopping with strength even makes a difference.

data.name: 0010 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: So, I continued sweeping around the class- room…I can only wonder how much time passed.

data.name: 0011 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I was mopping so frantically that I had lost any sense of time.

data.name: 0012 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I'd lost count of how many singularities I erased, but just as I finished one of them…

data.name: 0014 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Whoa!

data.name: 0015 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I was overwhelmed by blinding light and dizziness, and suddenly thrown into the hallway.

data.name: 0016 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I lost my sense of orientation and balance in the sheer immediacy of it.

data.name: 0017 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: As soon as I noticed, there was a hard linoleum corridor before my eyes.

data.name: 0018 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Ouch…

data.name: 0019 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Are the two of you unhurt?

data.name: 0020 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Do I look unhurt to you?

data.name: 0021 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It would appear that you are just fine.

data.name: 0022 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Yeah, exactly.

data.name: 0023 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: If there were a problem, it would be that my nose hurts like death.

data.name: 0024 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Or something as trivial as slight dizziness.

data.name: 0025 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Good grief, that was quite the experience.

data.name: 0026 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Oh, right, where's Nagato…?

data.name: 0027 (382.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Here.

data.name: 0028 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Unlike me, it seems she didn't burst out into the hallway like an idiot.

data.name: 0029 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Are you hurt anywhere?

data.name: 0030 (382.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: No issues.

data.name: 0031 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Aren't you at all worried about me?

data.name: 0032 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: It means the world to me to see you looking so well.

data.name: 0033 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: Yes, fortunately.

data.name: 0034 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: By the way, what happened? This is a normal place, right?

data.name: 0035 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: We do seem to be in the original space. Isn't that correct, Miss Nagato?

data.name: 0036 (382.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Yes. The original space and time. Abnormal space was destroyed.

data.name: 0037 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It seems that somehow, we were thrown out of that abnormal space when it disappeared.

data.name: 0038 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Is it safe to essentially assume we're in the clear?

data.name: 0039 (382.ja) KOIZUMI (古泉)
data.value: It certainly seems so, for the time being.

data.name: 0043 (382.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you all doing?

data.name: 0044 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Haruhi?!

data.name: 0046 (382.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What are you doing just sitting in the hallway? Plus your nose.

data.name: 0047 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Huh…?

data.name: 0048 (382.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: You've got a nosebleed.

data.name: 0049 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What?

data.name: 0050 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: I wiped my finger under my nose, and there was blood, just as Haruhi said.

data.name: 0051 (382.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: What were you doing? That's disgusting.

data.name: 0052 (382.ja) MONOLOGUE (モノロ)
data.value: Haruhi squinted her eyes at me with suspicion.

data.name: 0053 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: W-wait, you're misunderstanding!

data.name: 0054 (382.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Unbelievable, this is why you're--

data.name: 0055 (382.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Listen to me, I beg you!

data.name: 0056 (382.ja) INFO (CHOICE)
data.value: About Haruhi
